{"tid":1748024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日投票：有本土投本土，冇本土投泛民","createTime":"2019-11-23T13:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T07:26:21.000Z","uid":57911,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"08bf5387966896885a40700b73659dac2b68bf69","tid":1748024,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"固定原則：本土優先，不屌票，不分化，不鎅票，不信雷動，大局為重，泛民讓路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc4836f71e00f13916de4ff0e75403d2d19e52e","tid":1748024,"uid":57911,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"永遠記得下次投俾梁天琦，所以今次本土優先，係咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9973f65034b8b4dd1510c962a5341999ebd8370","tid":1748024,"uid":66283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:07:18.000Z","msg":"好簡單，一票不投保皇黨，唔好再聽網上賤種嘅分化言論<br />\n<br />\n用自己一票做個民意海嘯話俾國際社會聽，我哋不滿正苦我哋要改變，如果聽日結果同之前差唔多，即係代表抗爭者嘅聲音係小數，即係代表大家覺得保皇黨控制立會冇問題"},{"pid":"32230467a4e7e6be5e08fd76e53cddf786991758","tid":1748024,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【急】請手足傳給撞區候選人！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>活動申請不反通知書，先發表就出線有票，遲發表要退選。</span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FpzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=a7da2f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、民主派議員、及候選人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推一推行動post拉！連登重有邊個唔去投票！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】"},{"pid":"11b13dab63b4aec059fea96d15d980b8bdcee0b1","tid":1748024,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e1497bdaf25fff0c852ba61bd0f12982d1b7a0","tid":1748024,"uid":57911,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4cc4836f71e00f13916de4ff0e75403d2d19e52e","tid":1748024,"uid":57911,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"永遠記得下次投俾梁天琦，所以今次本土優先，係咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"本土讓夠，泛民係時候大局為重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9978e841900158cd734a3da7bc11dbdf79284ec3","tid":1748024,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ba76206357c6d3e5f511d95deb99058f96ebb9","tid":1748024,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:20:26.000Z","msg":"香城online玩家大型活動 投票Challenge<br />\n<a href=\"https: